            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美国知名媒体娱乐公司华纳兄弟探索集团（Warner Bros. Discovery）宣布其全球串流平台 Max 将于 2024 年 11 月 19 日正式登陆香港及东南亚市场。此次扩展象征著 Max 继美国、拉丁美洲及欧洲成功推出后，进一步进军香港、台湾、新加坡、马来西亚、印尼、菲律宾及泰国等 7 个新市场。Max 汇聚了多个深受全球观众喜爱的品牌内容，包括华纳兄弟、HBO、DC 宇宙、卡通频道等，为用户提供多元化的娱乐体验。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269310" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/maxinsoutheastasiata-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/maxinsoutheastasiata-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/maxinsoutheastasiata.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>订阅 Max 即可观赏  HBO、哈利波特、DC 宇宙、卡通频道、Max 原创系列等广受欢迎的品牌；亦有多部荷李活热门电影、Discovery 频道、TLC 、AFN、Food Network、探索调查频道 Investigation Discovery 和 HGTV 的精彩节目。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269312" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269313" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom</p><p>Max 以其丰富的剧集、电影及纪录片著称，当中包括多部热门作品如《哈利波特（Harry Potter）》系列、《老友记（Friends）》、热门同名游戏改编剧集《最后生还者（The Last of Us）》、《龙族前传（House of the Dragon）》以及《沙丘瀚战：第二章（Dune: Part Two）》。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269328" style="text-align: center;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_friends-694x540.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="540" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_friends-694x540.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_friends-1156x900.jpg 1156w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_friends-scaled.jpg 1157w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《老友记（Friends）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_002-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_002-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_002-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《沙丘瀚战：第二章（Dune: Part Two）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269315" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_001-694x366.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="366" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_001-694x366.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_001-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《沙丘瀚战：第二章（Dune: Part Two）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269323" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《最后生还者（The Last of Us）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269324" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-1-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-1-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-1.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《最后生还者（The Last of Us）》</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269325" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-2-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-2-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-2.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《最后生还者（The Last of Us）》</p><p>此外，Max 原创内容亦备受期待，如《沙丘：预言（Dune: Prophecy）》及 James Gunn 和 Peter Safran 上任 DC 宇宙后最新推出的成人动画《Creature Commandos》。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_tea-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_tea-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_tea.jpg 607w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《沙丘：预言（Dune: Prophecy）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_jih-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_jih-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_jih.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《沙丘：预言（Dune: Prophecy）》</p><p>用户订阅 Max 后亦可观赏儿童品牌 Cartoon Network 和 CARTOONITO，<br />容，由《探险活宝（Adventure Time）》、《熊熊遇见你（We Bare Bears）》、《Tom and Jerry》、《乐一通（Looney Tunes） 》到《少年悍将 GO！（Teen Titans Go!）》等应有尽有。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269330" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《探险活宝（Adventure Time）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1269331" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《探险活宝（Adventure Time）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269332" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《乐一通（Looney Tunes） 》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269333" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《乐一通（Looney Tunes） 》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269334" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_001-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《Tom and Jerry》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_002-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《Tom and Jerry》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1269336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_001-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《熊熊遇见你（We Bare Bears）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1269337" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_002-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《熊熊遇见你（We Bare Bears）》</p><p>从 11 月 19 日起，订户可透过 Max.com 官方网站及指定合作伙伴选择不同的订阅方案，并享有包括多个独立帐户及个人化推荐功能的升级观影体验。此外，儿童用户亦可享有专属帐户及家长监控功能，提升家庭使用便利性。随著 Max 的登陆，香港用户将能够在各种装置上轻松享受这个全新串流平台带来的视听盛宴。现有 HBO GO 订户将会于 11 月 19 日自动成为 Max 订户，Max 将于未来数星期将陆续公布更多详情。</p><h2>订阅方案：</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;"> </td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">标准方案</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">高级方案</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;">同时观看装置数：</td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">同时使用 2 部装置观看</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">同时使用 4 部装置观看</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;">影片解像度：</td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">全高清影片解像度</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">4K UHD 和 Dolby Atmos（按影片而定）</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;">跨装置观看功能：</td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">跨装置观看功能，包括电视</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">跨装置观看功能，包括电视</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;">可下载影片数量：</td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">下载多达 30 套影片以便随时随地观赏</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">下载多达 100 套影片以便随时随地观赏（设有上限）</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/18/iphone16proreview/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 Pro Max 详细开箱影片，并非只「多了颗掣」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/iphone-16-%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97-pro-max-%e5%a4%96%e5%aa%92%e4%b8%8a%e6%89%8b%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac-%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-18-%e5%80%8b%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-apple-watch-s10-%e5%8f%8a-airpods-4/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 系列 Pro Max 外媒上手评测，港人最爱 18 个功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/07/gurman-apple-to-launch-new-m4-macs-and-ipad-mini-7-on-november-1/software/mac-os-x/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">M4 Mac、iPad mini 7 或于 11 月发布　同时推出 M4 Pro、Max 版 Mac 电脑</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/warner-bro-max-streaming-coming-to-hong-kong-19-november/movie-2/">华纳兄弟 Max 串流服务登陆香港　下月 19 日起有得睇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
