        </item>
        <item>
            <title>实惠「多谢支持」帖文被误解结业 　网民：结业潮「呃 Like」黑心 + IKEA 即出抽水文</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/pricerite/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pricerite</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/pricerite/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 08:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交网络]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Facebook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[IKEA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实惠]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1269178</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日（15 日）凌晨 0 时香港家私品牌实惠在 Facebook 张贴了一则 8 字帖文：「多谢各位　多年支持」引起网民热议。事缘因其日前刚刚推出周年优惠售出大量家具，有订购了家私的网民要求实惠「顶到月尾」，因为其预订的梳化尚未到货。最后实惠在今晨 9 点再发帖文，表示仅是开展新一轮减价。有网民认为实惠在结业潮下为「呃 like」发出这种帖文非常黑心。</p><p>实惠在今日凌晨 0 时发布以下帖文，下面有网民揣测其是否要「毕业」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269183" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_1-472x580.jpg" alt="" width="472" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_1-472x580.jpg 472w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_1.jpg 697w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 472px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/GQq6L92gWi9ZCNvN/">实惠 Facebook</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269203" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015150451-1-694x179.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="179" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015150451-1-694x179.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015150451-1.jpg 1092w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有网民询问实惠是否「完成历史任务，可以『毕业』了」<br />
图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/GQq6L92gWi9ZCNvN/">实惠 Facebook</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269216" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152956-694x115.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="115" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152956-694x115.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152956.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲订购了梳化的网友显得徬徨，图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/GQq6L92gWi9ZCNvN/">实惠 Facebook</a></p><p>香港知名网上讨论区 LIHKG 有网民发帖指，实惠在结业潮下利用这种形式「呃 Like」非常黑心，又斥实惠不应该在这个时势下开这种玩笑。下面有网民则回应表示担心实惠会结业，不知道应否继续订货。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269202" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_5-694x267.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="267" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_5-694x267.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_5.jpg 1123w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3803349/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269204" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_6-694x154.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="154" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_6-694x154.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_6.jpg 881w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/mioOtT">LIHKG</a></p><p>最终实惠在今日（15 日）早上 9 时正再发新帖文，表示仅是为新优惠价钱造势宣传，下面引来网民劣评如潮。有网民在下面回应指，已经没有信心再预订任何产品，担心此为「执笠」先兆。另外有网民客观分析，指实惠这次市场推广行动不济，更称自己已经订购了价值数千元货物，看见实惠的 8 字帖文会觉得紧张是人之常情。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015151400-396x580.jpg" alt="" width="396" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015151400-396x580.jpg 396w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015151400.jpg 615w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 396px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/gJ2rjqjWy8WzmhwU/">实惠 Facebook</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269206" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_8-694x115.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="115" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_8-694x115.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_8.jpg 781w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/gJ2rjqjWy8WzmhwU/">实惠 Facebook</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_9-694x267.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="267" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_9-694x267.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_9.jpg 780w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/gJ2rjqjWy8WzmhwU/">实惠 Facebook</a></p><p>事件亦引来 IKEA Facebook 专页小编出来抽水，发文表示今日是「国际小编感谢日」，帖文与实惠相似，但最后加上了「小编」两只细字，表示感激各方支持 IKEA Facebook 页面管理员。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152040-409x580.jpg" alt="" width="409" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152040-409x580.jpg 409w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152040.jpg 635w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 409px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/NJSrPY3tMKra5ZtN/">IKEA Facebook</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.pricerite.com.hk/hk/zh/storeInfo/">实惠官网</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/GQq6L92gWi9ZCNvN/">实惠 Facebook</a>、<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3803349/page/1">LIHKG</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/NJSrPY3tMKra5ZtN/">IKEA Facebook</a><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/01/facebook-icon/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Facebook 应用程式图示乱变色，原来是技术性错误</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/pricerite/life-tech/social-network/">实惠「多谢支持」帖文被误解结业 　网民：结业潮「呃 Like」黑心 + IKEA 即出抽水文</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/pricerite/life-tech/social-network/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
